EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0900Z TO 1900Z DAILY UNTIL
   05 MAY WITHIN:
   A. 33 MILES OF 57-14.5N 008-29.0W.
   B. 22 MILES OF 57-33.9N 010-16.1W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1065/13.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 052000Z MAY 13.
